NIC Types

ENI - basic networking
EN - single route io virtulization/high performance.
    SR-IOV - allows single network device to present itself
    as multiple virtual devices to the operating system
    and hypervisor.
    Higher io while minimizing CPU utilization.
    Supports up to 100Gbps

    Intel VF interfaces support up to 10Gbps

Elastic Fabric Adapter (EFA) - HPC and Machine learning apps
    - Offers OS-Bypass - HPC and ML can communicate directly with the network interface
    hardware.